description:
Dark Horse Comics is proud to present The Perry Bible Fellowship: The Trial of Colonel Sweeto and Other Stories by acclaimed cartoonist Nicholas Gurewitch.

The award-winning Perry Bible Fellowship has a achieved a cult following both online and in its weekly appearances in newspapers and magazines around the world. Now, for the first time, the hilarious cartoons of Nicholas Gurewitch are being collected in this handsome hardcover edition.
name: HC

description: This Digital Exclusive features OVER 150 PAGES of fun! It's time for mischief and mayhem! Li'l Jinx is a feisty little girl ready to stir up trouble. Join Li'l Jinx and her friends Charley, Greg, Russ, and more as they live life to the fullest! Can her poor father keep up with her? Find out with 150 pages of classic Li'l Jinx, and a special sneak preview of Jinx: Little Miss Steps, her new graphic novel-where she's not so li'l anymore!
